  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Before we tell you-- before I'll tell you about Auschwitz, I have a very important things to tell you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Sonderkommando, what I told you, had a connection with an SS, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that this particular SS will get a bottle of diamonds, [INAUDIBLE] just say a bottle of diamonds.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This means because the Sonderkommando had in the hands when they-- things they had it in the hand, all kind of stuff, and diamond was the smallest thing to have in a small place hidden.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told him you get this particular, probably millions involved, but you have to give us rubber gloves, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] heavy-duty scissors, and guns.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If it comes to a point when the six months is over-- because they knew after six months, they'd be destroyed, they should try to cut the wire, try to kill somebody, try to run, and nothing to lose anyway.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew he has to be destroyed anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the kapo, who was a Jewish, Polish Jew, when they-- every six months they changed the Sonderkommando, they didn't changed him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German trusted him so much, they let them alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this son of a bitch, to say, he found out about the plan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he reported this to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was only four months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This could leave another two months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was, I would say, between September, October.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I cannot tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't have diary to mark down everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They already felt, they knew that they found out about the plan.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was four crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were connected with telephone wire, the four, underground, organized.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
